FivePoints.GraphNavigation

Class CoordinateMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • FivePoints.GraphNavigation.CoordinateMap

  • public class CoordinateMap
extends java.lang.Object
    CoordinateMap manages a set of nodes that are either occupied or free. When moving a whole object, the translation must only occupy blocks which are free, or else the translation refuses to execute.
